title: Lowest Female Suicide Rate
description: In 2021, Oman had the lowest female suicide mortality rate in the world, with only 0.21 suicides per 100,000 female population.

title: High Urban Population Growth
description: Oman experienced a significant urban population growth rate of 7.27% in 2023, one of the highest in the world.

title: High Population Growth
description: In 2023, Oman had a high population growth rate of 6.53%, ranking among the highest globally.

title: High Employment in Industry
description: As of 2023, 40.16% of Oman's total employment was in the industry sector, one of the highest proportions worldwide.

title: High Imports from Arab World
description: In 2023, 53.13% of Oman's total merchandise imports came from economies in the Arab World, one of the highest percentages globally.
